All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, List<E>, RandomAccess
public class GrowableArrayList<E>
extends ArrayList<E>

An ArrayList subclass that will never throw an IndexOutOfBoundsException and instead grow the backing array to match the size of the requested operation.
